\title{Improving Information Security Risk Management in Resource-Limited Universities using OCTAVE Allegro with Data Recovery Mechanism}

\author{
Fatima Amer\\
\small Department of Information Systems,\\
Faculty of Computer Science and Information Technology, Sana'a University, Sana'a, Yemen\\
