\textbf{Step} & \textbf{Target Verification Action} & \textbf{Assigned Role} & \textbf{Target Window} & \textbf{Technical Validation Criteria} \\
\midrule
1 & Network Partitioning and Malicious Node Isolation[cite: 11]. & Network Engineer & 30 Minutes & Confirm all external connections to the server rack are terminated[cite: 11]. \\
\addlinespace
2 & Clean OS Reinstallation and Database Server Setup[cite: 11]. & System Admin & 2 Hours & Validate core operational integrity and database engines[cite: 11]. \\
\addlinespace
3 & Retrieval and Decryption of Off-site Cloud Backup[cite: 5, 11]. & Database Admin & 1 Hour & Execute hash verification check against the backup manifest[cite: 11]. \\
\addlinespace
4 & SQL Database Restoration and Live Access Launch[cite: 11]. & IT Director & 30 Minutes & Verify concurrent student login and query functionalities[cite: 11]. \\
\bottomrule
\end{tabular}
